        {
            "name": "Cobble Mite",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Cobble Mite Pets",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Characters looking to keep a cobble mite as a pet can usually buy one in many large cities for 1 gp. Those who search for one in the wild must hunt carefully and risk finding enough cobble mites lairing together to form a cobbleswarm. A character with a familiar can choose a cobble mite, which must have the burrower familiar ability.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Bestiary 3",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Bestiary 3 pg. 52",
                                "alt": "Bestiary 3 pg. 52",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 66
                            },
                            "page": 52
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "advice_and_rules",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Advice and Rules",
                        "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                    },
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "burrower",
                            "alt": "burrower",
                            "game-obj": "Familiars",
                            "aonid": 2
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "text": "Cobble mites resemble squarish stones a few inches across with mouths like split geodes. Though indolent and harmless alone, they're dangerous in large groups.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Bestiary 3",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Bestiary 3 pg. 52",
                        "alt": "Bestiary 3 pg. 52",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 66
                    },
                    "page": 52
                }
            ]
        }
